channel.title: You do not have JDK installed - error?
channel.description:
Hello, I've downloaded Evilscape here and i want to load it on my own computer, so not for other ppl, just wanna test:) But when i wanna start it i don't really understand, If i start compile.bat and say to load server/compile server it says i don't have JDK installed?? I just downloaded & rebooted computer =S
Also if i just try to login it keeps saying i'm already logged in.
Getting this error when trying to login.
Server: ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:2514 Did not save for wizkid Server: ClientHandler: Client wizkid disconnected.
